Police
spokesperson Brigadier Motantsi Makhele said the three security officials had
been transporting money on behalf of a bank. After they got off the plane, the
armed men approached one of them and grabbed the bag of money from him. Although
all doors at the airport were locked immediately, the robbers escaped through
the main entrance, Makhele said.They
fired two shots on their way out and fled in an Audi and a Mercedes Benz. No
